{"about_the_game":"Atheria has fallen, All its people gone. When all is lost, they called for you. Trained by a mysterious immortal. Outcast from the city your grandfather founded, You alone must face 7 Demon Lords and their armies to save humanity. Discover the legacy of your ancestors and rescue the people of Atheria, For you are the last and only hope.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1887440/extras/Combat_Steam.gif?t=1692827753\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Combat</strong></h2>Learn and Master each fighting style to use against dynamic stat based enemies that grow more diverse as you level. Dodge, block and parry as you wait for openings.<br><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Seamlessly Combo melee attacks into skills and/or spells to create your own moves<br></li><li> Break the enemies poise or block, dodge and parry as you wait for an opening to counter<br></li><li> Weight system that dynamically effects attack and movement speed</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1887440/extras/Spells_Steam.gif?t=1692827753\" /><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Build your character and playstyle how you want - No Classes -No Hard Item restrictions<br></li><li> Procedural Stat based A.I. - Enemies grow more diverse and powerful as you level</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1887440/extras/Running_Steam.gif?t=1692827753\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Dungeons and Overworld Exploration</strong></h2> Journey through a fantasy overworld and delve into deadly dungeons to rescue the captured.<br><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Explore a hand crafted overworld full of life and dangers to discover<br></li><li> Delve into dark and ever-changing procedural dungeons<br></li><li> Rescue Villagers, Uncover Ancestral Lore, Learn Secrets that have been kept from you</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1887440/extras/Boss_Gif_Steam.gif?t=1692827753\" /><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Find Spell Books and Runes to learn and upgrade Spells, Skills and Fighting Styles<br></li><li> Set out on an Epic Adventure every time you leave town in a true Open World</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Other Key Features</strong></h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Procedural dungeons</strong> - Explore a different dungeon every time<br></li><li><strong>Crafting System</strong> - Craft Weapons, Food, Potions, Runes and more<br></li><li><strong>Skill based Combat</strong> - Time your dodges, blocks, spells and attacks or you won't survive<br></li><li><strong>Customization</strong> - Customizable Death Screen, UI and Enemy Health Bars<br></li><li><strong>Multi-staged Boss fights</strong> - Fight Epic Bosses that evolve during the fight<br></li><li><strong>Extensive Weapons</strong> - Find, buy or forge 100's of Unique weapons<br></li><li><strong>4 Armor Slots</strong> - Mix and Match 100+ pieces of armor (Helmet, Chest, Legs and Gauntlets)<br></li><li><strong>Enhanced Condition System</strong> - Light your enemies on fire or Shock your enemies in place!</li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1887440/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1692827753","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1887440/page.bg.jpg?t=1692827753","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1887440/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1692827753","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1887440/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1692827753","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[2,5],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","demos":[{"appid":2298870,"description":""}],"